<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Wasp" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Wasp,</orth> the insect Vespa: <bibl n="shak. luc 839" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 839</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.2.106" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. I, 2, 106</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 2.214" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. II, 214</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.329" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 329</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.814" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 814</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.132" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 132</bibl>. Emblem of petulant snappishness: <cit><quote>come, come, you w.; i' faith, you are too angry,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 2.210" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. II, 210</bibl></cit>.
